{
  "stem": "1502.5",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 169,
      "text": "The halls had bunks, the same way they had in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 170,
      "text": "You know, they had established the final solution.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 171,
      "text": "They must have established how the-- the quarters for Jews should look.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 172,
      "text": "It looked the same way.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 173,
      "text": "It was three, one on top of the other, the wooden-- the wooden bunks with their straw back.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 174,
      "text": "And they put me together with my family.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 175,
      "text": "We were in hall number 13.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 176,
      "text": "And it was full.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 177,
      "text": "I would say there were about 100 Jews in-- in that hall.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 178,
      "text": "I just want to mention a detail.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 179,
      "text": "People had delusions.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 180,
      "text": "Like, when I was on the truck with other Jews that I didn't know, I had never seen, I remember there was a family that they caught, name was Schubowitz.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 181,
      "text": "They were apparently very wealthy Jews.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 182,
      "text": "And this-- the father, Mr.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 183,
      "text": "Schubowitz, told me, you know, I will be out from the camp right away.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 184,
      "text": "Because I have very big connections.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 185,
      "text": "I'll be out with my family.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 186,
      "text": "So if you want to give me something for family that you have outside, you can give me a telephone number or something.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 187,
      "text": "Because I'll be out in no time.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 188,
      "text": "He was there with the wife and, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I think, two beautiful daughters, a very good looking young boy.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 189,
      "text": "They were very good looking and sweet people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 190,
      "text": "He told me that he has with him 600,000 francs in cash.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 191,
      "text": "Anyway, he arrived in-- in together with us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 192,
      "text": "They took away the 600,000 francs.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 193,
      "text": "They-- no connections of his helped.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 194,
      "text": "He was deported with the next transport with his entire family.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 195,
      "text": "He was in the same hall with us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 196,
      "text": "What happened the-- the next day in the-- in the hall, there was an SS, which I was-- I mention him in particular, because he was particularly brutal.",
      "word_count": 28
    }
  ],
